 Currency Converter – Frontend Capstone Project

 Project Overview

This is a React-based Currency Converter application built as part of a Frontend Capstone Project.

The application allows users to:
- Enter an amount
- Select a base currency
- Select a target currency
- Convert using real-time exchange rates

Exchange rates are fetched dynamically from the ExchangeRate-API.

 Features

- Real-time currency conversion
- Live exchange rate fetching
- Swap currencies functionality
- Error handling for invalid input
- Loading state while fetching data
- Responsive design (Desktop & Mobile)
- Clean and reusable component structure

Technologies Used

- React (Vite)
- Tailwind CSS
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- ExchangeRate-API
- Git & Github
